A lady took to the streets of Lagos to cause a serious scene as she fainted after begging her boyfriend to marry her. Eyewitnesses say the young lady was screeming and crying for her boyfriend to marry her or else she will die, as she fainted. It was also gathered that the lovers have been together for a long time which necessitated the woman to take such a decision. A young man with his clothes off, believed to be the boyfriend was heard crying, “this girl go put me for problem, what’s all this na, which kind scam be this”, as residents and passersby gathered. Watch the video below: Source